{"title":"乡情","authors":["李冬"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":3,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李冬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我放飞一只蝴蝶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点缀青青的山坡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小妹挥赶羊群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青脆的歌声消除寂寞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微风翻阅丢失的课本，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诉说童年的生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恰似天上云朵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我凝视飘然落叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒满宁静的村落。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖母点燃炉火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袅袅的炊烟绕梁而过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细雨打在无华的房檐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹奏农家的欢乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正如地里风车。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往日的故事已经枯黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小妹早已远嫁他乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖母可得安详，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心中好不怅惘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有那歌声依然清脆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袅袅炊烟绕过房梁。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}